title: Check Out These Photos Of Bani J Looking Absolutely Stunning At A Shoot
text:
Divya Rao Mar . 16 . 2017 
Bani J will always be one of my favourite girls – she’s real, unabashedly honest, and couldn’t give two hoots about what anybody thinks of her. She’s got an incredibly large fan base on social media and was one of the finalists on Bigg Boss 10 . While we continue to miss seeing her on TV, here are some gorgeous photos of her from a shoot to help you get through the day.
